org.sql: SELECT spree_stock_items.* FROM spree_stock_items INNER JOIN spree_stock_locations ON spree_stock_locations.id = spree_stock_items.stock_location_id WHERE spree_stock_items.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_stock_locations.active = "$1"
